# ITARA Sports Analytics Platform

**Professional football intelligence system for the East African market.**

## 🚀 Deploy to Streamlit Community Cloud (Free)

### Step 1 — Create a GitHub Repository
1. Go to [github.com](https://github.com) and create a **new public repository** (e.g. `itara-analytics`)
2. Upload **both files** from this folder:
   - `app.py`
   - `requirements.txt`

### Step 2 — Deploy on Streamlit Cloud
1. Go to [share.streamlit.io](https://share.streamlit.io)
2. Sign in with your GitHub account
3. Click **"New app"**
4. Select your repository: `your-username/itara-analytics`
5. Set **Main file path** to: `app.py`
6. Click **"Deploy!"**

> ⏱️ Deployment takes ~2 minutes. Your app will be live at:
> `https://your-username-itara-analytics-app-xxxxxx.streamlit.app`

