## 📦 Features Included

| Feature | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| 🏠 Dashboard | KPIs, charts, radar analysis, squad overview |
| 📊 Data Management | Excel upload, manual entry, match result logging |
| 🏆 League Table | FIFA/UEFA points system (W=3, D=1, L=0) with charts |
| ⚖️ Player Comparison | Side-by-side metrics + radar overlay + ITARA verdict |
| 🧠 Coach Decision Center | Starting XI selector, risk analysis, position reports |
| 🏥 Health Reports | Fitness monitor with availability thresholds |
| 🤖 Agent Intelligence | xG, xA, market valuation, potential ratings |
| 📤 Export Center | Excel (multi-sheet), PDF report, CSV |

## 📐 Analytics Formulas Used

- **CPR** (Composite Player Rating): `0.40×PI + 0.20×G/M + 0.15×A/M + 0.10×PassAcc + 0.10×Health + 0.05×ProgScore`
- **Market Value**: `V = PI × κ × (1 + ΔM) × age_factor` — κ = RWF 1,250,000
- **xG**: Shots-on-Target × conversion rate (λ=0.32)
- **xA**: Assists weighted by pass accuracy
- **Progressive Score**: Dribbles + Tackles per match composite

## 🏟️ Excel Upload Format

Your Excel file should include these columns:
```
Player, Team, Position, Age, Goals, Assists, Matches, Minutes_Played,
Shots_on_Target, Pass_Accuracy, Dribbles_Completed, Tackles_Won,
Health_Score, Performance_Index
```
Missing columns will be auto-filled with defaults.

